overview: Farmer Stinky Thumbs Arbuckle is a man obsessed with catching and killing the elusive Skunk Ape. Old Stinky Thumbs is hot on the trail when a group of horny coeds cross his path. Will Stinky Thumbs Finaly have his revenge? Will the busty coeds pop there bikini tops? See Wrath of The Skunk Ape to find out! Written and Directed by Mike Hartman (Heavy Mental, Blood Orgy at Beaver Lake)
title: Wrath of the Skunkape
